name: RZ Shear (2.1)
description:
A heavy paper cut and diorama aesthetic feel who can provides great inspiration for your handcrafted creations or for producing outstanding art pieces.

The "getting started" prompts are located on the model preview pictures.

Before starting, load your favourite negative or use this one :

(bad art), (poorly drawn), (extra limbs), (close up), strange colours, (blurry), blur,boring, sketch, lackluster, signature, letters, watermark, big tits, big boobs, big chest, (frame), low resolution

Shear ext is avaiable on my GUMROAD, featuring :

  • A different 704*704 trained dataset & settings

  • More than 20 quality prompts

Note that Shear Ext is not intended to be superior; it's a distinct approach that relies more on personal preference and feels. It still offers a more subtle integration to more complex prompts and less foliages / woods.

Quick preview comparing and combining Shear with Shear EXT with minimal prompting :

"An illustration of a beautiful ((village in the snow)) in a rz-shear art style"

"An illustration of a (city at night) in a rz-shear art style"

An illustration of a beautiful (forest in the night with a view on the moon) in a rz-shear art style

If you want more isolated scenes, start your prompts with 3d tokens, such as smooth 3d illustration, octane render, 3d render and such. Papercut works very well with thoses aswell

Happy generations everyone !

romerorz.art - Twitter - DeviantArt - Gumroad
